    <h2>Welcome</h2>
    <p>The Department of Ophthalmology and Visual Sciences established the Ophthalmic Clinical Trials and Translational Center (OCTTC) to provide services in clinical trials and translational studies that evaluate preventive, therapeutic, and diagnostic interventions in ophthalmic diseases. Located on the second floor of the Illinois Eye and Ear Infirmary, the center acts as a liaison between principal investigators and sponsors. </p>
    <p>&nbsp;</p>
